{"type": "article", "id": 25559, "title": "看图：这里是过去24小时内发生的重要的事", "description": "每天我们都会摘取重要的新闻图片。", "date": "2016-04-16T14:52:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 5792, "name": "熊本"}, {"id": 26326, "name": "世越号"}, {"id": 3559, "name": "上海时装周"}], "category": 5, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 29, "praise_count": 131, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607101249kzAQlOFgcvMTYLBi.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>过去的一段时间里，你需要知道的有：</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><b>1、日本熊本震后</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071012370rCULEwNBtPKXbJS.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">jijipress/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<p class=\"\">熊本城在地震中损毁严重。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101238Eaqhne45V0RIk29K.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.80092593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">jijipress/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101239iMfgcnPH8YBoQwm5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">KAZUHIRO NOGI/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101239VwnjWqOogx4GTys5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">KAZUHIRO NOGI/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">当地居民行走在废墟之中。16 日凌晨，熊本市又发生了一起 7.3 级地震。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>2、“世越号”沉船事故纪念活动</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101240rK2TukXOWQyZcFNh.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63796296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Yonhap/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">韩国京畿道，安山高中学生会联合主办“世越号”沉船事故两周年纪念活动，学生们把对遇难者想说的话写在卡片上。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071012417ogL8kYAuC0IwHRM.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68611111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Yonhap/视觉中国</p></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">2014 年 4 月 16 日上午，韩国一艘载有 476 人的“世越号”客轮在全罗南道珍岛郡海域发生浸水事故，之后沉没。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>3、“蜘蛛与苍蝇”</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101241mRXUCKZEaNWxse5z.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">NASA 发布“蜘蛛与苍蝇”星云 IC 417 的“蜘蛛”部分图片。这一星云距离地球有一万光年的距离。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>4、印度渔民</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101241L2qcDpFKny7tw4z3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">ASIF HASSAN/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">巴基斯坦卡拉奇（Karachi），印度渔民被巴基斯坦海事安全局拘捕。<br></p>\n<h2>上海时装周闭幕</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><b>1、品牌秀场</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101242nkdpvtf3rWy1RqMP.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">秀场上的童模。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101242XwKfOmg8xkYvSGVI.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101243la9j8mFd0vgentRc.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">郭长耀/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101243JWQ4sn5tUKCyfF6R.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">郭长耀/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>2、街拍</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101244nrHxS5o3YMBwFeEN.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">摄影师U.K/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101244LTZqaQdWmrkUMFbB.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">摄影师U.K/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101245MGFAQVjL8r2e5qBX.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">摄影师U.K/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101246RlrI7T48OyNKMStV.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">上海新天地附近的“潮人”们。</p>\n<h2>除此之外，这些也值得一看：</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><b>1、泥地嬉戏</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101246qlZ4QX3BxFrgHGP5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64722222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">ISHARA S.KODIKARA/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">斯里兰卡 Kirindiwela，儿童在泥地中参加传统游戏，庆祝僧伽罗人和泰米尔人新年。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>2、泰国宋干节</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101247dwgD7PRcrSCF1jQh.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">LILLIAN SUWANRUMPHA/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">泰国曼谷，民众在街头参加“水枪大战”，庆祝宋干节。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>3、小黄人沙雕</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101247T6Nf5bCBkYPdoUVG.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65648148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">路透社/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">哈萨克斯坦阿拉木图（Almaty）举行“Sand Fantasy”沙雕艺术节，一名男子在以《神偷奶爸》为主题的作品上喷洒防护胶水。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>4、狮子的合家福</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101248LsAIQd0gwYq1cHPl.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">barcroftmedia/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">坦桑尼亚塞伦盖蒂（Serengeti），3 只母狮和 8 只幼狮在草地上休息。把家里的每个成员都聚集在一起休息绝非易事，但是这些狮子却配合默契，让摄影师拍下了完美的合影。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>5、晨雾缭绕</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101248i7HM4DwCNRQ1POT5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63888889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">李长华/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">贵州省榕江县古州镇高董苗寨，雾气腾升使这个古老的苗寨好像一幅美丽画卷。 <br></p>\n\n\n"}